{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/contentinset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIEdgeInsets","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@UIEdgeInsets"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"contentInset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is equal to "},{"code":"UIEdgeInsetsZero","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", viewport"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"properties such as "},{"code":"centerCoordinate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" assume a viewport that matches the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view’s frame. Otherwise, those properties are inset, excluding part of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"frame from the viewport. For instance, if the only the top edge is inset, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map center is effectively shifted downward."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the map view’s superview is an instance of "},{"code":"UIViewController","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" whose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"automaticallyAdjustsScrollViewInsets","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the value of this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property may be overridden at any time.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The usage of "},{"code":"automa